definition: abbr. for the Philippines 菲律賓|菲律宾[Fei1 lu:4 bin1]
(bird species of China) Philippine cuckoo-dove (Macropygia tenuirostris)

sentences.english: Thailand, Malaysia and the Philippines are considering new price controls or subsidies.
sentences.chinese: 泰國，馬來西亞以及菲律賓都在考慮價格控制和補貼。

sentences.english: The election is the Philippines' first using an electronic vote-counting system.
sentences.chinese: 這此選舉是菲律賓第一次採用電子計票系統。

sentences.english: Marila is the capital of the Philippine.
An island of the west-central Philippines south of Luzon. It was first visited by Spaniards in1570.
sentences.chinese: 民都洛島菲律賓中西部一島嶼，位於呂宋島以南。

sentences.english: Over one hundred and twenty thousand Filipinos live and work there.
sentences.chinese: 超過十二萬菲律賓人居住和工作在那。

sentences.english: BUY, Buy more American obsolete weapons, then re-sale them to the Philippines.
sentences.chinese: 買吧，多買點美國過時的武器吧，再賣點給菲律賓。

sentences.english: I attended high school and college at the University of the Philippines and I graduated with a degree in Accountancy.
sentences.chinese: 我在菲律賓就讀高中及大學，並且得到會計學士學位。

sentences.english: Typhoon Megi is the strongest storm the Philippines has faced for four years.
sentences.chinese: 颱風“鮎魚”是菲律賓近四年所遭受的最強颱風。

sentences.english: Tzu Chi volunteers in the US and the Philippines carry out regular free dental clinics for the needy residents.
sentences.chinese: 美國和菲律賓慈濟志工爲貧困的人舉辦義診活動。

sentences.english: Jade vine is native to the Philippines where it grows in tropical rain forests.
sentences.chinese: 綠玉藤原產地在菲律賓的熱帶雨林中。

sentences.english: There was no reason why the Philippines should not have been one of the more successful ASEAN countries.
sentences.chinese: 菲律賓沒有理由無法成爲亞細安比較成功的國家之一。

sentences.english: Philippines Senator Aquilino Pimentel says ASEAN countries also are in a position to help.
sentences.chinese: 菲律賓參議員皮門特爾說，東盟國家也可以提供幫助。

sentences.english: I had no clear idea of the progress of fighting in the Philippines.
sentences.chinese: 當時我對於菲律賓戰事的進行狀況並無明確印象。

sentences.english: The Philippines faced political instability after 1946.
sentences.chinese: 菲律賓在1946之後面臨政局不穩定。

sentences.english: The disease is also spreading through India and the Philippines.
sentences.chinese: 亞洲的印度和菲律賓國內也出現了麻疹病毒的蔓延。

sentences.english: The Philippines is getting impatient, Mr. del Rosario said.
sentences.chinese: 羅薩里奧說，菲律賓開始失去耐心。

definition: South Korea (Republic of Korea)/Han, one of the Seven Hero States of the Warring States 戰國七雄|战国七雄[zhan4 guo2 qi1 xiong2]/Korea from the fall of the Joseon dynasty in 1897
